==English==
===Proper noun===
'''[[Moldavian]] [[Soviet Socialist Republic|SSR]]'''
# Moldavian Soviet Socialist Republic, the name for the [[Moldova|Republic of Moldova]] while under the rule of the [[Soviet Union]] (1940-1941 and 1945-1991).

====Translations====
{{top}}
*Moldovan: [[РСС Молдовеняскэ]] (RSS Moldovenjaskz)
{{mid}}
*Romanian: [[RSS Moldovenească]]
*Russian: [[Молда́вская ССР]] (Moldávskaja SSR)
{{bottom}}

